claim: 50 Cent has yet to release Animal Ambition.
premise_source_doc_sentence: All 11 tracks on the standard edition were issued as singles prior to the album 's release ; in order , they are `` Do n't Worry ` Bout It '' , `` Hold On '' , `` Pilot '' , `` Smoke '' , `` Hustler '' , `` Chase the Paper '' , `` Everytime I Come Around '' , `` Irregular Heartbeat '' , `` Winners Circle '' , `` Twisted '' , and `` Animal Ambition '' .
